  "idmlContentBlocks": [
    "WPF window UI make user easier to follow instruction.",
    "BIM WORK",
    "Work with the team to design and document complex office tower across multiple plots. The project use extensive amount adaptive family to resolve non-conventional panel layout.",
    "50+ buttons and commands in Rhino UI using python and Rhino Commons.",
    "Work seamlessly with the EnneadTab for Revit on more integrated solution, without requirement on user end to know grasshopper or Rhino.Inside.",
    "A large portion of the collection works also dedicated to the Rhino workflows specifically over a variety of common pain points in modeling and management.",
    "Using Eto modeless forms and DisplayPipeline, the instruction is given to the users on a narrative way to reduce front-load training time.",
    "For better control on the complex family, internal formulas are designed to function like small program that can work with the external script for the max efficiency.",
