    "Managing 16 buildings in a new office, residential and cultural complex. Due to the complexity of the geometry and limited team member skill set, many customized python scripts was developed to run manually or automatically to assist modeling, data management and other workflows. The project specific automations were later restructured to the office collection.",
    "Help team to explore mutiple non-stacking-grid module strategies in Dynamo. The script layout and apply detailed revit family over complex curtain wall relationship. The rule-reading-logic is designed with ease of reading in mind so all designer can utilize it.",
